::KitKat::

She walked back to base.  She saw Stringtra and Quickstrike talking.  
She didn't want to interupt them, so she walked by without saying 
anything to them.  She went inside and sat down at Darkmouse's 
console.  She wan't the best with computers, but she was wanting to 
get familar with the scanners.  She studied them and learned how to 
work them.  She was hoping to crack the mouse's codes so she could 
run the console as well if the situation called for it.  She found 
the the mouse had put in security systems that she couldn't break 
into.  She sat back and sighed a bit.  She was getting restless 
again.  She needed a good hunt.  But Quickstrike had ordered no one 
leave untill Megatron returns. "Oh what a yawn a minute day."
